236
00:13:52,917 --> 00:13:53,918
BOJKOT BRADLEY – VRAH

237
00:14:18,109 --> 00:14:19,152
Dobré ráno, Bradley.

238
00:14:20,403 --> 00:14:21,404
Nastup.

239
00:14:24,490 --> 00:14:25,491
Jasně.

240
00:14:31,122 --> 00:14:34,375
Teď jedeme do skladiště,
